Garden Plan for Two 4×32 Raised Beds (Markdown Download)

Location: Dripping Springs / Dallas area (Zone ~8b)  
Beds: Two raised beds, 4 ft × 32 ft each, oriented east–west (north long edge)  
Soil: Imported high‑quality raised‑bed mix (deep, loose, high organic matter)  
Irrigation: Drip lines with 1 GPH emitters; soaker lines for beans and carrots  
Baseline transplant window: mid‑March (adjust ±10–14 days to your microclimate)  
Tomato varieties: Plum Regal, Juliet, Viva Italia, Sungold, Cherry 100

